features: 5-Tier Shoe Racks: Haiice shoe rack is suitable for a family with 2-3 people or a person living alone to store 4-5 pairs of shoes. For the corner at home, it is a good choice for you and children to increase space by being placed vertically.

Open Design: Compared with a shoe box, this plastic kids shoe rack is easy to take. You do not need to open the door and take shoes conveniently. Four plastic panels form a stable structure, making the shoe rack sturdy.

Multi-functional Use: The shoe rack uses in the entryway, dorm, teen's room, or living room. And you can use the top tier as a storage rack to put the key or plant. And the White-Grey color is easily matching the style of many American houses.

Water-proof & Rust-prevention: The plastic shoe organizer is made from ABS plastic and is water-proof and rust preventive, so it is easy to clean dust and mud. And the lightweight feature makes it easy to carry.

Assemble Easily: The package box includes an English instruction, so you install the shoe rack step by step with it. The rack can store slippers, high heels, flat shoes, or sneakers (it is suitable for 5.2‘’ height shoes).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The best feature of the product is that it is a vertical design that is a space saver and has a small footprint. I can easily place all kinds of shoes from crocs, trainers, and mid-top hikers. Many options before discovering this product are usually horizontal designs, which would take up a lot of space I do not have. I have this right next to my garage door coming into the house and opted for the six shoe pair version. It assembles quickly by snapping all the arms into place & placing holding pads, took less than 10 minutes. It is a convenient design that has been durable after a few weeks of use. One benefit unbeknownst to me was that it shows why you need this product. After retrieving and placing shoes worn everyday, it is evident that all the nasty substances such as dirt, pet hair, & all the other gunk that sticks to your shoes falls on the holding pads. And because the holding pads are white, you can see right away why it is not a good idea to wear shoes into the house after they have been worn all day out in the streets. Shoes are totally unsanitary. I am able to clean this product easily by spraying with a water hose outside and drying it off. Our family is working towards going shoe-free in the house and seeing the benefits of its functionality, easy maintenance & assembly, space saving, and convenience, I am going to be purchasing a second one. I am planning on zip-tying them together to connect them. Excellent product, highly recommended, and going to buy another.
